name: Ext.draw.sprite.AnimationParser
doc: Computes an intermidiate value between two values of the same type for use in animations. Can have pre- and post- processor functions if the values need to be processed before an intermidiate value can be computed (parseInitial), or the computed value needs to be processed before it can be used as a valid attribute value (serve).
short_doc: Computes an intermidiate value between two values of the same type for use in animations. ...
